<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Class for managing the rendering of 3D objects in a scene. </para>



<para>The <link linkend="_classexample_1_1_view">View</link> class handles updating and rendering the objects in a scene. It uses a camera to calculate the view matrix, a light for shading, and a color buffer and rasterizer for rendering the scene. </para>
</section>
